{{#*inline "title"}}MFA Enabled | Twennie{{/inline}}
<div class="success-container">
  <h1 class="success-title">Multi-factor authentication is enabled!</h1>
  <p class="success-message">Save these <strong>recovery codes</strong> in a safe place. Each can be used once if you lose access to your authenticator app.</p>

  <ul class="individual-membership-access-list">
    {{#each recoveryCodes}}<li><code>{{this}}</code></li>{{/each}}
  </ul>

  <div class="success-actions" style="display:flex; gap:.75rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <a href="{{dashboard}}" class="success-button">return to my dashboard</a>
    <a href="{{baseUrl}}" class="success-button" style="background:#777;">manage mfa settings</a>
  </div>
</div>
